&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity for a Band 5 registered nurse has arisen on our 22 bed Respiratory Ward.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an enthusiastic nurse who can work dynamically and at a fast pace to ensure safe and effective care delivery. The post is open to both junior nurses (with a minimum one year post reg experience) or experienced nurses who wish to learn more skills in respiratory care. We have close links with the high dependency unit and will give opportunities to develop skills in tracheostomy care, non-invasive ventilation, high flow oxygen and chest drains. You will work with highly skilled Respiratory Ward nurses and closely with the respiratory specialist nurses, together, delivering a high standard of care to the respiratory patient.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Alyshea Gibson, Ward Sister&lt;/p&gt;
